---
layout: base.njk
title: Raddirnar
description: Hverjir segja hvað í ESB-umræðunni? Skoðaðu fullyrðingar eftir stjórnmálaflokkum, samtökum og einstaklingum.
wide_layout: true
---

<h1>Raddirnar</h1>
<p>Hverjir taka þátt í ESB-umræðunni og hvað segja þeir? Hér má skoða fullyrðingar eftir stjórnmálaflokkum, samtökum og einstaklingum — og hversu vel þær standast skoðun.</p>

{% set parties = [] %}
{% set individuals = [] %}
{% for entity in entities %}
  {% if entity.type == "party" %}
    {% set parties = (parties.push(entity), parties) %}
  {% elif entity.type == "individual" %}
    {% set individuals = (individuals.push(entity), individuals) %}
  {% endif %}
{% endfor %}

{% if parties | length %}
<section class="entities-section">
  <h2>Stjórnmálaflokkar</h2>
  <div class="entities-grid">
    {% for entity in parties %}
    <div class="entity-card entity-card--{{ entity.stance | replace('pro_eu', 'pro') | replace('anti_eu', 'anti') | replace('mixed', 'mixed') }}">
      <div class="entity-card-header">
        <h3 class="entity-card-name">{{ entity.name }}</h3>
        {% if entity.stance == "pro_eu" %}
        <span class="entity-stance stance-pro">ESB-jákvæð</span>
        {% elif entity.stance == "anti_eu" %}
        <span class="entity-stance stance-anti">ESB-gagnrýnin</span>
        {% else %}
        <span class="entity-stance stance-mixed">Blandað</span>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
      <p class="entity-card-desc">{{ entity.description }}</p>
      {% if entity.articles | length %}
      <div class="entity-card-articles">
        <strong>Birtist í {{ entity.articles | length }} greiningu{{ "m" if entity.articles | length > 1 else "" }}:</strong>
        <ul>
          {% for slug in entity.articles %}
          {% for report in reports %}
          {% if report.slug == slug %}
          <li><a href="/umraedan/{{ report.slug }}/">{{ report.article_title }}</a></li>
          {% endif %}
          {% endfor %}
          {% endfor %}
        </ul>
      </div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

{% if individuals | length %}
<section class="entities-section">
  <h2>Einstaklingar</h2>
  <div class="entities-grid">
    {% for entity in individuals %}
    <div class="entity-card entity-card--{{ entity.stance | replace('pro_eu', 'pro') | replace('anti_eu', 'anti') | replace('mixed', 'mixed') }}">
      <div class="entity-card-header">
        <h3 class="entity-card-name">{{ entity.name }}</h3>
        {% if entity.stance == "pro_eu" %}
        <span class="entity-stance stance-pro">ESB-jákvæð</span>
        {% elif entity.stance == "anti_eu" %}
        <span class="entity-stance stance-anti">ESB-gagnrýnin</span>
        {% else %}
        <span class="entity-stance stance-mixed">Blandað</span>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
      {% if entity.role %}<p class="entity-card-role">{{ entity.role }}{% if entity.party %} ({{ entity.party }}){% endif %}</p>{% endif %}
      <p class="entity-card-desc">{{ entity.description }}</p>
      {% if entity.articles | length %}
      <div class="entity-card-articles">
        <strong>Birtist í {{ entity.articles | length }} greiningu{{ "m" if entity.articles | length > 1 else "" }}:</strong>
        <ul>
          {% for slug in entity.articles %}
          {% for report in reports %}
          {% if report.slug == slug %}
          <li><a href="/umraedan/{{ report.slug }}/">{{ report.article_title }}</a></li>
          {% endif %}
          {% endfor %}
          {% endfor %}
        </ul>
      </div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

<section class="entities-note">
  <p><em>Þessi síða er í þróun. Eftir því sem fleiri greinar eru greindar bætast fleiri aðilar við og fullyrðingar þeirra tengjast sjálfkrafa.</em></p>
</section>
